name: Milton Data Duck
description: This needs to live somewhere. When I was about 10 years old, our teacher handed out these provincial government safety booklets about the dangers of smoking, strangers, and drugs. The back page was a comic called "Milton Data Duck" about a duck that lived in a computer, similar to Max Headroom. One of the panels warned us about the effects of drugs and included an unsettling image of his eyes on fire. It's been over 30 years and I still think about it.
